"This command <action>opens a dialog box for renaming the collection</action>."
msgstr ""
"Cette commande <action>ouvre une boite de dialogue pour renommer la "
"collection</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:495
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>U</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Collection Fields...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>U</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Champs de la collection...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:505
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>opens the <interface>Collection Fields Dialog</"
"interface></action>."
msgstr ""
"Cette commande <action>ouvre la boite de dialogue des <interface>Champs de "
"la collection</interface></action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:511
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Generate Reports...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Générer des rapports...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:518
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>opens the <interface>Report Dialog</interface></action> "
"for generating reports about the collection."
msgstr ""
"Cette commande <action>ouvre la boite de dialogue <interface>Rapport</"
"interface></action> pour générer des rapports à propos de la collection."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:524
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bibliography</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Convert to Bibliography</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bibliographie</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Convertir en bibliographie</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:532
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>converts a book collection to a bibliography</action> "
"by adding certain fields necessary for Bibtex export, and it is only enabled "
"when a book collection is open."
msgstr ""
"Cette commande <action>convertit une collection de livres en bibliographie</"
"action> en ajoutant certains champs nécessaires à l'exportation vers BibTeX. "
"Elle n'est disponible que pour les collections de livres."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:538
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bibliography</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>String Macros...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bibliographie</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Ligne de Macros...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:546
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>opens a dialog box for editing the Bibtex string "
"macros</action> in the collection. It is only enabled when editing a "
"bibliography."
msgstr ""
"Cette commande <action>ouvre une boite de dialogue pour modifier les macros "
"BibTeX</action> de la collection. Celle-ci n'est accessible que lors de "
"l'édition d'une bibliographie."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:552
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bibliography</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Check for Duplicate Keys</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bibliographie</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Vérifier les doublons</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:560
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>checks for duplicate Bibtex keys</action> and can "
"filter the collection to show the entries with duplicated keys."
msgstr ""
"Cette commande <action>recherche les clés BibTeX en double</action> et peut "
"filtrer la collection pour afficher les entrées ayant des clés en double."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:566
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bibliography</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Copy Bibtex to Clipboard</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bibliographie</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Copier au format BibTeX vers le presse-papiers</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:574
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>copies a Bibtex citation</action> to the clipboard so "
"that it can pasted in a LaTeX document."
msgstr ""
"Cette commande <action>copie une citation BibTeX</action> vers le presse-"
"papiers pour être collée dans un document LaTeX."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bibliography</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Cite Entry in Lyx</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bibliographie</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Citer l'entrée dans LyX</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:588
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>sends a citation for the selected entries</action> to "
"the so-called <emphasis><link linkend=\"hidden-bibtex-options\">lyxpipe</"
"link></emphasis> for use in <application>LyX</application>, "
"<application>Kile</application>, or other LaTeX applications. It is only "
"enabled when editing a bibliography."
msgstr ""
"Cette commande <action>envoie une citation pour les entrées sélectionnées</"
"action> vers <emphasis><link linkend=\"hidden-bibtex-options\">lyxpipe</"
"link></emphasis> pour servir dans <application>LyX</application>, "
"<application>Kile</application> ou d'autres applications LaTeX. Celle-ci est "
"activée seulement lors de l'édition d'une bibliographie."

